    "name": "时空噜比",
    "steam_appid": 3254910,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/03775a7db527d4cf4f42479e2d19caf7.poster.avif?t=1772330747\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/03775a7db527d4cf4f42479e2d19caf7.webm?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时空噜比拥有独特的能力：可将时间倒流最多 3 秒。利用这项力量，你能逃离陷阱、修正失误、破解谜题。手握沙漏，每一秒都至关重要——你的目标是守护蜜蜂，这些小小生命正是维系生态平衡的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/de9e30b8a8785ea1ee2d4b6bccce2a59.poster.avif?t=1772330747\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/de9e30b8a8785ea1ee2d4b6bccce2a59.webm?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/de9e30b8a8785ea1ee2d4b6bccce2a59.mp4?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/d295de694cdf7c825d83724366701df1.poster.avif?t=1772330747\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/d295de694cdf7c825d83724366701df1.webm?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将操控噜比——一颗携带着上古沙漏的魔法种子，掌握着倒转时间的力量。你的使命是拯救蜂巢，它们是地球生命得以延续的根基；同时，逆转环境崩坏，为濒危的大自然争取重生的希望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/ecaf4075087c0bb74dd85d6c3b278637.poster.avif?t=1772330747\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/ecaf4075087c0bb74dd85d6c3b278637.webm?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/ecaf4075087c0bb74dd85d6c3b278637.mp4?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/bf5fe947feff8bbe0fbaf85447dfadc1.poster.avif?t=1772330747\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/bf5fe947feff8bbe0fbaf85447dfadc1.webm?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越四个遭遇生态灾难的独特世界：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >野火肆虐的森林 —— 昔日的栖息地已被烈焰吞噬</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >毒素弥漫的废土 —— 空气与水源正在腐蚀生命</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工业化侵蚀的荒原 —— 大地与绿意逐渐被钢铁吞没</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失控科技统治的未来 —— AI与机器无视生态法则</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/d7a0eec15b6b791e8cc8343e645da8b0.poster.avif?t=1772330747\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/d7a0eec15b6b791e8cc8343e645da8b0.webm?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/d7a0eec15b6b791e8cc8343e645da8b0.mp4?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/90459f0d0061c755c838dddcdc6a62d9.poster.avif?t=1772330747\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/90459f0d0061c755c838dddcdc6a62d9.webm?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >噜比不仅是种子，它还会播种。在旅途中，你将营救遇到的友好种子，它们会在特殊关卡中登场。你可以将它们种下、培育，解锁全新能力，为冒险带来转机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/3cbae4302d68d413bbf781fc6f51582e.gif?t=1772330747\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/3cbae4302d68d413bbf781fc6f51582e.poster.avif?t=1772330747\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/90b68cc614f1e662226f916b2ddff05b.poster.avif?t=1772330747\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/90b68cc614f1e662226f916b2ddff05b.webm?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《时空噜比》适合所有玩家。你可以选择放松体验，专注于解谜与收集；也可以挑战高难度速通，成为真正的时间守护者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/1102c38eaaae0f67abfc2b5a1bf08678.poster.avif?t=1772330747\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/1102c38eaaae0f67abfc2b5a1bf08678.webm?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254910/extras/1102c38eaaae0f67abfc2b5a1bf08678.mp4?t=1772330747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，每一次时光倒流，都是让自然重生的机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你，能否拯救未来？</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 繁体中文",
